    "# Lab 2.1: KV Caching Implementation\n",
    "\n",
    "## Objective\n",
    "Implement and compare different Key-Value (KV) caching strategies for transformer inference. Understand memory-performance trade-offs and implement advanced caching techniques.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Learning Goals\n",
    "1. Implement standard KV caching from scratch\n",
    "2. Compare memory usage across different caching strategies\n",
    "3. Implement PagedAttention-style memory management\n",
    "4. Profile cache performance and identify bottlenecks\n",
    "\n",
    "## Prerequisites\n",
    "- Completion of Week 1 labs\n",
    "- Understanding of transformer attention mechanism\n",
    "- Basic PyTorch and CUDA knowledge\n",
    "\n",
    "## Let's Begin!"
   ]
  },
